msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_CarryIce_Desc"
msgid ""
"A Gerudo named Pokki has collapsed in front\n"
"of the ancient shrine. You'll have to find a way\n"
"to revive her if you want to get inside. She was\n"
"barely coherent, but it sounded like she was\n"
"muttering about wanting to drink something\n"
"called <1.se_co>Noble Pursuit<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_CarryIce_Gerudo_CarryIce_Delivered"
msgid ""
"You delivered the ice to the owner of\n"
"the canteen.\n"
"\n"
"She's now able to make ice-cold Noble Pursuits.\n"
"She's asked that you go back to Pokki and let\n"
"her know that a drink is waiting for her.\n"
"Pokki had collapsed in front of the shrine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_CarryIce_Gerudo_CarryIce_Finished"
msgid ""
"When you told Pokki about the ice-cold Noble\n"
"Pursuit, she flew off in the direction of the\n"
"Gerudo canteen.\n"
"\n"
"You can enter the shrine anytime you want."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_CarryIce_Gerudo_CarryIce_Get"
msgid ""
"You got Anche to give you some ice!\n"
"\n"
"You now have to carry the ice back to Furosa,\n"
"who waits at the exit of the ruins north of town.\n"
"With the blazing heat of the desert, it'll be a \n"
"challenge to <1.se_co>get back without the ice melting<2.re_co>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_CarryIce_Gerudo_CarryIce_bar"
msgid ""
"Noble Pursuit is a famous drink from the\n"
"Gerudo canteen. Unfortunately, it can't be\n"
"made right now because they're all out of ice.\n"
"\n"
"You'll need to go to the icehouse north of\n"
"Gerudo Town and ask Anche to give you some\n"
"ice. You can only get Anche's help while it's\n"
"bright out, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Gerudo_CarryIce_Name"
msgid "The Perfect Drink"
msgstr ""

